{"title":"Doves Cry, New State 4130 Purple Reign All-Road SS","link":"https://bikerumor.com/doves-cry-new-state-4130-purple-reign-all-road-ss/","date":1684259804000,"content":"<p>State Bicycle Co. has just updated their affordable 4130 All-Road fixed gear, single speed. The new Purple Reign edition dons a <a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/collections/4130-steel-bikes/products/4130-purple-reign-fixed-gear-single-speed\" target=\"_blank\">new colorway</a> that is striking, and ranks it up there with “The Beautiful Ones”, without question. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>State Bicycle Co. 4130 All-Road Bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Purple Reign front side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-front-side.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all photos c. State Bicycle</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This “Darling Nikki” of an update also includes redesigned geometry. They’ve increased tire clearance moving up to fit a “Prince”-ly 700x45mm tire, thanks to the tig-welded “wishbone” rear. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Purple Reign new bigger tire clearance\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-bigger-tire-clearance.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The larger tire capacity and massive clearance long-reach brakes should make it the perfect choice for riders to think “Baby, I’m a Star”…or city commuters, grocery-getters, and anyone that rides less-than-perfect roads. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Purple Reign new colorway\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-new-colorway.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Purple Reign seatpost\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-seatpost.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Purple Reign’s super-durable, double-butted 4130 Chromoly frame and fork with the single-speed drivetrain will make for a trouble-free and low-maintenance steed that’s steeped in reliability. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Purple Reign all-road drops\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-all-road-drops.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Purple Reign Wide Riders\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Purple-Reign-Wide-Riders.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can choose what bars the bike comes with, State’s All-Road gravel Drops or the Wide Riders. The tubeless compatible tires are mounted to a pair of wheels that roll on sealed bearing hubs with a rear flip-flop hub. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Purple Reign – State 4130 All-Road Features &amp; Pricing</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $550 </p>\n\n\n\n<p>6 frame sizes are available to fit rider heights from 5’3″ to 6’7″</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frame: </strong>Double-Butted 4130 Chromoly Steel, TIG Welded w/ “Wishbone” Rear to Accommodate Big 700c Tires</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dropouts:</strong> Horizontal Dropouts ft. Integrated Chain-Tensioners</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheel Set: </strong> Tubeless compatible – All-Road (Track) Wheelset, Drilled 40 mm High-Flange Hubs w/ Sealed Bearings w/ 38x700c tires* (*not tubeless rated).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Hubs:</strong> Includes 16T Freewheel and Fixed Gear Cog – Easily Ride Fixed Gear or Single Speed</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Crankset:</strong> Steel Forged Crank w/ 130 BCD, 170MM Crank Arms, 46t Chain-ring</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Gearing:</strong> 46×16</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Handlebars:</strong> Choose All-Road Flared Gravel Drops or Wide-Risers</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brakes:</strong> Long Reach Brake Calipers</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Max Recommended Tire Size: </strong>45c</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out all of the bicycles that State offers that “Would Die 4 U”…by hitting the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s also an updated 4130 Flat Bar All-Road bike with a clutched rear derailleur, disc brakes, and a couple of two-tone fades for $900, if you’re into that sort of thing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">StateBicycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/doves-cry-new-state-4130-purple-reign-all-road-ss/\">Doves Cry, New State 4130 Purple Reign All-Road SS</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"c8e914815d200389c0a26bc932494ab053e01dd782b7f98330a9bcb91f131aa7","category":"Cycling"}